            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Why is liminality scary?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Lack of context/purpose</p>
        </div>

